TITLE: de_stability

AUTHOR: fleethefactory

CONTACT: mynamemightbecalvin@gmail.com

VERSION: V1

DATE RELEASED: Jan 26, 2013

Terrorists are attempting to destroy evidence of
building fertilizer bombs in an Iranian factory
compound. Help keep the region stable.
 
Counter-Terrorists: Enter the campus and prevent
the Terrorists from destroying any evidence. 

Terrorists: Blow up the storage depots in the 
campus.
 
Other Notes: There are two bomb sites.

Credits:
Designed by fleethefactory and guerillablood, and textured by 

fleethefactory.

CHANGELOG: 

- Expanded T spawn
- detailed out of bounds
- color correction added
- added much more detail to map interior
- street staircase expanded
- balcony added to A bombsite
- Lower Alley expanded, map interior is less open. 
- weird lighting issues fixed
- properly optimized
